00:01:22.910 --> 00:01:24.670 align:middle line:90%
It's an infinite journey.

00:01:24.670 --> 00:01:25.660 align:middle line:90%
There's no end, really.

00:01:25.660 --> 00:01:26.810 align:middle line:10%
It's an infinite journey.

00:01:26.810 --> 00:01:30.750 align:middle line:10%
