one step at a time.

00:01:30.750 --> 00:01:32.710 align:middle line:84%
And you can make the
journey too, Chantal.

00:01:32.710 --> 00:01:35.200 align:middle line:84%
It's not that
mysterious or mystical.

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:36.700 align:middle line:90%
Anybody can make this journey.

00:01:36.700 --> 00:01:38.110 align:middle line:84%
I got interested
in these things.

00:01:38.110 --> 00:01:41.980 align:middle line:84%
